      "text": "🎥 Click below for a short video to see what the job looks like: Computer Vision Engineer\nLogatec, Slovenia | Relocation support availableOn-site collaboration with the software, mechanical design and manufacturing team.\nAt Pek Automotive in Slovenia we design and build advanced autonomous electric systems and robotic vehicles used in demanding real-world environments such as agriculture and rescue operations. We are expanding our R&D team and looking for a Computer Vision Engineer who will enjoy developing computer vision based instruments for our powering next-generation autonomous machines.\nWhat you will work on:• Develop and implement algorithms for image processing,• Develop and implement image recognition algorithms,• Interact with the other members of R&D team for improving performance of produced and developed computer vision based systems.\nWhat we are looking for:• Experience in image processing and recognition,• Experience in optic systems selection for computer vision,• Implementing and testing computer vision algorithms.\nWhat we offer:• Work on real-world autonomous machines and robotics,• Relocation support and visa assistance for Slovenia,• A collaborative international engineering team,• Career growth and learning opportunities.",
      "$type": "com.linkedin.pemberly.text.AttributedText"
    },
